response: Alright! Let's go over what makes up the infinite combinations of your diamond that end up driving your diamond's price. These factors are called the 4Cs: cut, color, clarity and carat. Much like with a car with a certain cut (roadster, sedan, hatchback, minivan), color (white, yellow, red), clarity (tinted windows, all clear) and carat (engine, horsepower), think about what you want to get your wife-to-be. Just say cut, color, clarity or carat to learn more.
